1996.assessment:
July 1996 PDI headquarters attack — security forces/thugs attacked Megawati supporters;
dozens killed/disappeared. Aceh insurgency continuing. East Timor resistance ongoing.
Pre-crisis year with political tensions rising. Annual deaths hundreds across all theaters.

2019.assessment:
Papua/West Papua: TPNPB significantly escalated; worker killings in Nduga district;
KNPB/student protests; security crackdown. Post-election protests May 2019 (8 killed).
Annual deaths in Papua conflict rising. Low-moderate political violence nationally.
